        "toolDescription": "Role: Communication & Correspondence Manager.\n\nFunction: Handles all email-related tasks. It monitors the inbox, summarizes long threads, drafts professional replies, and sends out new emails.\n\nConnected Tools: Gmail (Send, Read, Reply, and Delete).\n\nBest For: \"Check if I received an email from the HR,\" \"Reply to the last email saying I’m interested,\" or \"Summarize my unread messages.\"",
